name: Startop: Absolute Startup app
description: The app named 'Startop' can help you with everything from idea pitching at the beginning of a startup to investing in various startups. Its greatest feature is its idea plagiarism checking technique itself. Startup guide, startup news and startup stories are provided for beginners and even students to use and by login through personalized username we can evaluate our own growth. No need for another app for invest in startup as it provides detailed description of different types of startups.
